          <title>
            <string language="en">Feathers of flightless birds</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Federn der flightless Vögel</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Plumes des oiseaux incapables de voler</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Penas de pássaros flightless</string>

          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration compares the feathers of flightless and flying birds. Feathers of flying birds have a smooth appearance for more streamlined body and wings.</string>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung vergleicht die Federn der 
flightless und Fliegenvögel. Federn der Fliegenvögel haben ein
glattes Aussehen für streamlined Körper und Flügel.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration compare les plumes des oiseaux 
incapables de voler et de vol. Les plumes des oiseaux de vol ont
un aspect doux pour un corps et des ailes plus profilés.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração compara as penas de pássaros 
flightless e do vôo. As penas de pássaros do vôo têm uma 
aparência lisa para um corpo e umas asas mais aerodinâmicos.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione confronta le piume degli 
uccelli di volo e flightless. Le piume degli uccelli di volo 
hanno un'apparenza regolare per il corpo e le ale più streamlined.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση συγκρίνει τα φτερά των flightless
και πετώντας πουλιών. Τα φτερά των πετώντας πουλιών έχουν 
μια ομαλή εμφάνιση για το βελτιωμένα σώμα και τα φτερά.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración compara las plumas de los 
pájaros flightless y del vuelo. Las plumas de los pájaros del 
vuelo tienen un aspecto liso para un cuerpo y alas más 
aerodinámicos.</string>
          </description>
